Currently with the new {{DefaultPluggableProjectOperation}}, plugin developers need to implement the {{getLabelHtml()}}, which is usually just an i18n lookup. However, this involves either creating a new velocity template just for the label, or injecting {{I18nResolver}} and HTML encoding the lookup result, which can easily be forgotten.

So it would be nice to change {{DefaultPluggableProjectOperation}} or provide a subclass that provides a method to accept a label key and substitute parameters and generate the label HTML.

